target_text: Atiyah who urged a strategy of creating a quagmire for U.S. forces in Iraq, buying time for Al Qaeda\u2019s headquarters to rebuild its strength in Pakistan. \u201cProlonging the war [in Iraq] is in our interest,\u201d Atiyah said in a letter that upbraided Jordanian terrorist Abu Musab al-Zarqawi for his hasty and reckless actions in Iraq
